msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.str.rstrip"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.rstrip:1
msgid "Remove trailing characters."
msgstr "移除尾随字符。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.rstrip:3
msgid ""
"Strip whitespaces (including newlines) or a set of specified characters "
"from each string in the Series/Index from right side. Replaces any non-"
"strings in Series with NaNs. Equivalent to :meth:`str.rstrip`."
msgstr ""
"从 Series/Index 中每个字符串的右侧剥离空格（包括换行符）或一组指定字符。"
"将 Series 中任何非字符串替换为 NaN。等效于 :meth:`str.rstrip`。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.rstrip
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.rstrip:8
msgid ""
"Specifying the set of characters to be removed. All combinations of this "
"set of characters will be stripped. If None then whitespaces are removed."
msgstr ""
"指定要移除的字符集。该字符集的所有组合都将被剥离。如果为 None，则移除空格"
"。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.rstrip
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.rstrip:17
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.str.strip`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.rstrip:18
msgid "Remove leading and trailing characters in Series/Index."
msgstr "移除 Series/Index 中的前导和尾随字符。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.rstrip:20
